<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="calm-v">calm <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /kɑːm/    美 /kɑːm/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(使) 平静；平静下来</strong></h4>
<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="calm-down">calm down</h3>
<p>1.<strong>(使) 平静下来； (使) 镇静下来：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I placed the chick in the nest, and it quickly calmed down.
我把小鸟放到窝里，它很快平静了下来。</p><footer>2017 全国</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>When he gets upset, he will take a few deep breaths to <strong>calm himself down</strong>.
心烦时，他会深深地吸几口气以使自己平静下来。</p></div></div>